"use strict";(self.webpackChunkmedishift_deployment_server=self.webpackChunkmedishift_deployment_server||[]).push([[157],{2538(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"tableOfContents":["The Paperwork of Temporary Staff","The Risks and Inefficiencies of Manual Management","InteriMed\xae: Your Centralized Dashboard","Free Yourself from Repetitive Administrative Tasks"],"content":[{"title":"The Paperwork of Temporary Staff: A Headache for Pharmacies","paragraphs":["The administrative management of temporary staff represents a considerable challenge for Swiss pharmacies. This time-consuming process involves a multitude of tasks: searching for candidates, verifying qualifications, managing contracts, tracking timesheets, adjusting payroll, and ensuring legal compliance.","These tasks are added to an already substantial administrative burden for pharmacies, which must handle the establishment\'s secretarial work, participate in the billing process, process orders, manage inventory, and draft various pharmaceutical documents.","According to a recent survey, administrative simplification is indeed the primary expectation of human resources directors in the healthcare sector, highlighting a pressing need to which temporary staff management adds another layer of complexity."],"image":"https://unsplash.com/photos/person-using-macbook-pro-npxXWgQ33ZQ","imageCaption":"Traditional administrative management consumes valuable time in pharmacies"},{"title":"The Risks and Inefficiencies of Manual Management: An Avoidable Burden","paragraphs":["Manual management of temporary staff exposes pharmacies to several risks and inefficiencies that can have significant consequences:","\u2022 Potential errors in payroll and compliance processes, which can lead to legal or financial complications","\u2022 Considerable time consumed by administrative staff, which could be allocated to higher value-added tasks such as patient counseling","\u2022 Difficulty in obtaining a clear overview of the use and costs of temporary staff, complicating budget planning","\u2022 Challenges in ensuring that all temporary staff comply with specific regulatory requirements for each canton","Navigating cantonal regulations for temporary healthcare staff proves particularly complex. For example, the authorization process for replacements in the canton of Vaud involves several specific steps, with variable documentary requirements, while the canton of Valais has its own rules regarding the presence of pharmacists."]},{"title":"InteriMed\xae: Your Centralized Dashboard for Temporary Staff","paragraphs":["InteriMed\xae radically transforms the administrative management of temporary staff in pharmacies through an intuitive and comprehensive digital platform. Key features that simplify administration include:","\u2022 Digital profiles of professionals with verified qualifications, eliminating the need for repetitive manual checks","\u2022 Streamlined booking and confirmation process, reducing time spent on coordination","\u2022 Automated notifications and reminders for upcoming assignments, minimizing the risk of oversights","\u2022 Digital timesheets and billing/payment integration, significantly simplifying financial management","\u2022 Centralized record-keeping of temporary assignments, facilitating reporting and analysis","\u2022 Integrated compliance checks, ensuring adherence to specific cantonal regulations","The platform also offers analytical features allowing pharmacies to identify trends in their use of temporary staff, predict future needs, and optimize their personnel budgets, thus transforming a simple booking tool into a strategic workforce management aid."],"image":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80","imageCaption":"The InteriMed\xae platform centralizes and simplifies all administrative management"},{"title":"Free Yourself from Repetitive Administrative Tasks with InteriMed\xae","paragraphs":["By adopting InteriMed\xae for managing your temporary staff, your pharmacy can achieve significant gains in terms of efficiency and quality:","\u2022 Reduction of time spent on administrative tasks by 60 to 80%, allowing your team to focus on value-added activities","\u2022 Decrease in administrative errors thanks to process automation, improving payroll accuracy and regulatory compliance","\u2022 Better visibility of temporary staff costs and utilization, facilitating budget planning and resource optimization","\u2022 Simplification of compliance with cantonal regulations, reducing legal risks","\u2022 Improvement of the overall experience for both pharmacies and temporary professionals, fostering positive working relationships","In a context where pharmacies are increasingly called upon to expand their healthcare service offerings while maintaining operational efficiency, simplifying administrative processes becomes an essential performance lever. InteriMed\xae allows you to free up valuable time and resources to focus on what truly matters: the health and well-being of your patients."]}],"keywords":["pharmacy administrative management","HR simplification Swiss healthcare","pharmacy management software","InteriMed staff administration","pharmacy process automation"]}')}}]);